mainText:
I'm sorry. Truly sorry. The world needed him longer. You guys who are left need to carry it on. Improvise. Innovate like he did. And choose the most charismatic showman you've got for the presentations. It doesn't have to be the
 CEO- those are big shoes to fill and it's a hard job.

The rest of us will be rooting for you as we mourn the passing of a giant.&nbsp;
